<br>
Hunted there this morning with myself (level 10 Cleric, dinged 11), Junun (13 Wizard) and Neozion (12 Pally). Fights were hard but exp and loot were both excellent. This area will support a full group in this level range as the wolves are also nearby and only slightly higher in level.<br>
<br>
Basically, you can base out of Adribard's and hunt from 9 through the low 20's without ever having to leave if you want. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
